Package: securetools
Title: Security-Hardened Tool Library for R LLM Agents
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Ian", "Flores Siaca", , "ian.flores.siaca@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Pre-built tool definitions for common data science operations
    with built-in security constraints. Tools are returned as
    'securer::securer_tool()' objects with path scoping, parameterized SQL,
    domain allow-lists, size limits, and rate limiting. Designed for use
    with 'securer' sandboxed R code execution.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/ian-flores/securetools
BugReports: https://github.com/ian-flores/securetools/issues
